+    /* ane/lxa logging levels (snapshot module v1.3) and maincpu_jammed (v1.4,
+       VICE commit 573f0f38a2 "save 'jammed' status into snapshot") were
+       inserted between last_opcode_info and maincpu_ba_low_flags. A snapshot
+       written by an older x64sc (module v1.2, e.g. a release build) lacks
+       them; reading them unconditionally misaligns ba_low_flags and the
+       interrupt sub-modules, raising SNAPSHOT_READ_OUT_OF_BOUNDS_ERROR. Guard
